T1  - Policy Contagion: What Do We Learn From Financial Reforms?
AU  - Li, Nan
AU  - Papageorgiou, Chris
AU  - Xu, Tong
AU  - Zha, Tao
Y1  - 2026/02/01
PY  - 2026
