T1  - Strategic Flip-Flopping in Political Competition
AU  - Fournier, Gaëtan
AU  - Grillo, Alberto
AU  - Tsodikovich, Yevgeny
Y1  - 2026/02/01
PY  - 2026
DA  - 2026/02/01
