AU  - Dioikitopoulos, Evangelos V.
AU  - Varvarigos, Dimitrios
Y1  - 2026/02/01
PY  - 2026
DA  - 2026/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.70004
T2  - International Economic Review
